gross
and net written premiums in 2007 both increased 2% over the respective totals in 2006. adjusting for the sale of mendota in both years, net written premiums in the personal
insurance segment in 2007 increased 4% over 2006, driven by continued strong retention rates and increases in renewal price changes, partially offset by a decline in new business volume. gross and net
