pretax unrealized investment gains at december31, 2007 increased by $258million over year-end 2006, primarily driven by the fixed maturity
portfolio. the increase in net unrealized investment gains on fixed maturities was primarily driven by the impact of declining market interest rates on both taxable and tax-exempt
