postretirement benefit aspects of collateral assignment split-dollar life insurance arrangements (eitf06-10). eitf06-10 provides
guidance on the recognition and measurement of assets related to collateral assignment split-dollar life insurance arrangements. eitf06-10 is effective for fiscal years beginning
after december15, 2007. the company does not expect the adoption of eitf06-10 effective january1, 2008 to have a material effect on its results of operations,
financial position or liquidity.
