in june 2007, acsec issued statement of position 07-1, clarification of the scope of the audit and accounting guide investment
companies and accounting by parent companies and equity method investors for investments in investment companies (sop07-1). sop07-1
provides guidance in determining whether an entity is within the scope of the aicpa audit and accounting guide investment companies. it also addresses
